text: Julian Ocleppo and Andrea Vavassori were the defending champions but only Vavassori chose to defend his title, partnering Andrea Pellegrino.https://www.itftennis.com/procircuit/players/player/profile.aspx?PlayerID=100170193 Vavassori lost in the semifinals to Ivan and Matej Sabanov. Sabanov and Sabanov won the title after defeating Sergio Galdós and Juan Pablo Varillas 6–4, 4–6, [10–5] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw San Benedetto Tennis Cup - Doubles 2019 Doubles
